data.description: This beautiful 3661 sq ft ranch style home features an open concept with vaulted ceilings and double sided fireplace connected to the large master complete with master bath and huge walk in closet. The basement is plumbed for a wet bar. This home has many updates including new carpet upstairs, new tile, newly painted fence & deck, and new landscaping for this low maintenance yard. This like NEW home can be yours for an amazing $88/sq ft!!
